Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California Coast!

Name: The Atlantic Bridge, Averoy, Norway
Description:
A chain of bridges connecting islets, and communities 
adorned with sheep flocks and midnight sunsets

Name: Palace of Culture and Science, Warsaw, Poland
Description:
A beautiful view point of the city in what was once Stalinist architecture is 
now a thriving and almost progressive center point for 21st century Poland.

Name: Cukiernia Koch, Sczczecin, Poland
Description:
The  most excellent panzki (donut) in a humble bakery off the coast 
of a baltic fjord. Possibly the best worldwide.

Name: Katedrála Sv. Víta, Prague, Czech Republic
Description:
Awesome cathedral in the palace center. Features include stunning 
stain glass, and art which demand an aire and atmosphere of reverence.

Name: Ponte di Rialto, Venice, Italy
Description:
This bridge liberates access across the grand canal of Venezia, Italy.
 Cruising the splender of the canal on foot or gondola, the sun 
caressess a city layout from 421 AD in all it's beauty.
